column5: Due to the forecasted high SW winds we are forced to cancel the tournament that was scheduled for tomorrow (Aug 9). There are many small boat anglers interested in participating. We are going to postpone the tournament until Sunday Aug 16th, 2009.  Sorry for the inconvenience, but I hope this will save a few on gas driving down in the morning.  Please pass the word on to those interested. We will see you on the 16th.
